column5: I'm looking for the dates and contact info for Sask Landing Walleye derby and the Duncairn dam derby..Thanks

I have a page on my site at www.getfish.net that has the dates and to access it directly go to http://getfish.net/swt99/index.htmthat will put you right on to the page for the Saskatchewan Walleye TrailHope to see you out there this summer,Russ
